Usage: pack_module_model_libs [-help] [-cell <string>] [-only_files <string>]
                              [-validate]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>           # <module name> (string, optional)
-only_files <string>     # <list of files> (string, optional)
-validate                # <diff befor and after pack libs> (bool, optional)